m/3-ne/28.html?verse=1#p1">3 Nephi 28:1</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note7-"><span class="label">7. </span><p data-aid="136100533" id="note7_p1"><a class="cross-ref" href="/manual/teachings-joseph-smith/chapter-34" old-href="../../../../manual/teachings-joseph-smith/chapter-34.html"><em>Teachings of Presidents of the Church: Joseph Smith</em></a> (2007), 393–94.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note8-"><span class="label">8. </span><p data-aid="136100535" id="note8_p1">See <a class="scripture-ref" href="/scriptures/nt/james/1.5?#4" old-href="../../../../scriptures/nt/james/1.html?verse=5#p5">James 1:5</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note9-"><span class="label">9. </span><p data-aid="136100537" id="note9_p1"><a class="cross-ref" href="/manual/teachings-joseph-smith/chapter-10" old-href="../../../../manual/teachings-joseph-smith/chapter-10.html"><em>Teachings: Joseph Smith</em></a><em>,</em> 132.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note10-"><span class="label">10. </span><p data-aid="136100539" id="note10_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" href="/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.33?#32" old-href="../../../../scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.html?verse=33#p33">Doctrine and Covenants 121:33</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note11-"><span class="label">11. </span><p data-aid="136100540" id="note11_p1">See <a class="scripture-ref" href="/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.5?#4" old-href="../../../../scriptures/bofm/moro/10.html?verse=5#p5">Moroni 10:5</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note12-"><span class="label">12. </span><p data-aid="136100541" id="note12_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" href="/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.61?#60" old-href="../../../../scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.html?verse=61#p61">Doctrine and Covenants 42:61</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note13-"><span class="label">13. </span><p data-aid="136100543" id="note13_p1">Neal A. Maxwell, “<a href="http://speeches.byu.edu/talks/neal-a-maxwell_meek-lowly">Meek and Lowly</a>” (Brigham Young University 